snippet.textDisplay: Bitch PLEASE don’t bleach the roots again. Use toner PLEASE. Too much bleach on your scalp can make your hair fall out. TRUST ME PLEASE we have very similar hair and if you have a sensitive scalp like I do, putting too much bleach on it in a short period of time can damage your follicles and you can get a lot of hair loss that takes years to grow back if you’re lucky. You can order the shimmer lights purple shampoo from sallys and just let it sit on your hair while you do everything else in the shower and then tone it again if it’s still too brassy. Having your hair be a little brassy for a little bit is soo much better than having hair loss in the long run. I love you Sarah but PLEASE don’t torture your scalp like that
